# 📝 Simple Note-Taking App

A lightweight and minimalist web-based note-taking application built with Node.js, Express, and MongoDB. Users can add, view, and delete notes through a simple frontend interface.

---

## 🌐 Live Demo

> _Optional: Add your deployed link here (e.g., Render, Vercel, Railway)_

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🧾 Add new notes
- 📋 View all existing notes
- ❌ Delete notes
- 💾 MongoDB for persistent storage
- ⚡ Simple and responsive UI using HTML/CSS/JavaScript

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Backend:** Node.js, Express
- **Frontend:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- **Database:** MongoDB (local or Atlas)
- **API:** RESTful routes

